|---------|--------|-----------|-----------|-----------|
| [[Active]]  | [[{{_Pa'al_}} of קדש]] | [[{{_Pi'el_}} of קדש]] | [[{{_Hif'il_}} of קדש]] | [[{{_Hispa'el_}} of קדש]] |
| [[Passive]] | _Nif'al_ | [[{{_Pu'al_}} of קדש]] | [[{{_Huf'al_}} of קדש]] | \^ |

